        <mj-section>
            <mj-column vertical-align="middle">
                <mj-text mj-class="paddit">Hello {firstName}&comma;</mj-text>
                <mj-text mj-class="heading">We&apos;re thrilled to share some exciting news with you &mdash; we have officially acquired Swifton Solutions&comma; a move that significantly expands our capabilities and deepens our commitment to delivering cutting&dash;edge technology solutions&period;</mj-text>
                <mj-image align="center" width="600" src="assets/images/rapid-swifton.png" alt="We have officially acquired Swifton Solutions" title="We have officially acquired Swifton Solutions" />
                <mj-text mj-class="paddit"><a href="https://swifton.co.uk/" target="_blank" title="Swifton Solutions &dash; Tailored Software&period; Trusted Partnerships&period;">Swifton Solutions</a>&comma; brings a strong track record of expertise in &period;NET and Azure environments&comma; aligning perfectly with our core focus areas&colon; digital transformation&comma; data integration&comma; and artificial intelligence&period; With their deep experience across the Microsoft technology stack&comma; this acquisition strengthens our ability to design and deliver scalable&comma; secure&comma; and high-performance solutions tailored to the needs of Local Authorities&period;</mj-text>
                <mj-text mj-class="paddit">Importantly&comma; both our teams share a strong commitment to using non-proprietary&comma; open architecture technologies wherever possible&period; This allows us to develop leaner&comma; more maintainable applications that reduce overheads&comma; avoid vendor lock&dash;in&comma; and ultimately deliver better long-term value for the public sector&period;</mj-text>
                <mj-text mj-class="paddit"><a href="https://swifton.co.uk/" target="_blank" title="Swifton Solutions &dash; Tailored Software&period; Trusted Partnerships&period;">Swifton</a> will continue to operate with its own dedicated team of developers&comma; focusing on private sector clients while bringing fresh technical capabilities into our broader offering&period;</mj-text>
                <mj-text mj-class="paddit">Their <a href="https://swifton.co.uk/solutions/" target="_blank" title="Swifton Solutions &dash; Tailored Software&period; Trusted Partnerships&period;">core solutions</a> include&colon;</mj-text>
                <mj-text mj-class="paddit"><ul>
                    <li>Custom CRM Systems</li>
                    <li>ERP Integration</li>
                    <li>Health &amp; Safety Assessment Platforms</li>
                    <li>Bespoke Software Development</li>
                </ul></mj-text>
                <mj-text mj-class="paddit">We see this as a powerful step forward &mdash; giving us the flexibility to support more complex and cost&dash;conscious public sector projects&comma; without compromising on innovation or quality&period;</mj-text>
                <mj-text mj-class="paddit">If you&apos;d like to learn more or explore how these enhanced capabilities can benefit your organisation&comma; we invite you to <a href="https://swifton.co.uk/" target="_blank" title="Swifton Solutions &dash; Tailored Software&period; Trusted Partnerships&period;">visit Swifton&apos;s website</a> or get in touch to set up a conversation&period;</mj-text>
                <mj-text mj-class="paddit">Thank you for your continued trust and partnership&period;</mj-text>
                <mj-text mj-class="paddit">The Rapid team&period;</mj-text>
            </mj-column>
